@startuml
actor App 
box "Runtime"
participant Orchestrator
database GlobalNode
database LocalNodes
end box

App -[#green]> Orchestrator: Request:\nModel list (different algorithms and/or hyper-parameters),\ndata, filters, transformation

== Training phase==
Orchestrator -[#blue]-> Orchestrator: Control:\nTrain model 1
ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode :Training algorithm for model 1
GlobalNode -[#red]> GlobalNode: Store:\nModel 1

Orchestrator -[#blue]-> Orchestrator: Control:\nTrain model 2
ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode :Training algorithm for model 2
GlobalNode -[#red]> GlobalNode: Store:\nModel 2
... Repeat ...

== Testing phase==
Orchestrator -[#blue]-> Orchestrator: Control:\nTest model 1
ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode :Prediction algorithm for model 1
GlobalNode -[#red]> GlobalNode: Store:\nMetrics for model 1

Orchestrator -[#blue]-> Orchestrator: Control:\nTest model 2
ref over Orchestrator, LocalNodes, GlobalNode :Prediction algorithm for model 2
GlobalNode -[#red]> GlobalNode: Store:\nMetrics for model 2
... Repeat ...

Orchestrator -[#green]> App: Response:\nFinal result
@enduml
